snippet.description:
The Little Lebowski. Btw, this here is the original video, I made it. I've seen quite some re-uploads from other people on youtube, instagram, facebook and whatnot. Not that I mind that it's making its rounds, I'm just saying this is the original, that's all.


____________________________________________________________________
My second channel, Tim Turbo, a weird webseries a la Rick and Morty (it's in german though): https://www.youtube.com/c/timturbo
____________________________________________________________________


Here's some random things I'll write to be easily found by search engines and stuff: Priest baptism dunking baby water holy water the big lebowski. where's the money lebowski. jeff bridges.
This baptism in Georgia is enough to make your head spin - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aFGHerqhSC8
This is baptism an insane baptism of the child.
snippet.title: WHERE'S THE MONEY LEBOWSKI
